Holyfield has since rebuilt his relationship with Tyson and they recently appeared at Village East Cinema in New York for a screening of new documentary Champs, which tells their story, and that of Bernard Hopkins.

Directed by Bert Marcus, Champs focuses on the aforementioned trio's rise from poverty to the top of the sport.

